text: Carlos Quintana may refer to: *Carlos Quintana (boxer) (born 1976), Puerto Rican boxer *Carlos Morales Quintana (born 1970), Spanish architect and yachtsman, husband of Princess Alexia of Greece and Denmark *Carlos Quintana (baseball) (born 1965), former baseball player *Carlos Quintana (footballer) (born 1988), Argentine football defender
